adwa\u0144ski | pos=MF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no= 9|nat=POL||name=[[Marcin Robak]] | pos=FW|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=POL||name=[[Rafa\u0142 Wolszty\u0144ski]]| pos=FW|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=POL||name=Konrad Gutowski | pos=FW|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=POL||name=Bart\u0142omiej Poczobut | pos=MF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=18|nat=POL||name=[[Daniel M\u0105ka]] | pos=MF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=20|nat=GER||name=[[Christopher Mandiangu]] | pos=FW|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=POL||name=[[Patryk Wola\u0144ski]] | pos=GK|other=}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=23|nat=POL||name=[[\u0141ukasz Kosakiewicz]] | pos=DF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=24|nat=POL||name=[[Wojciech Paw\u0142owski]] | pos=GK|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=25|nat=POL||name=\u0141ukasz Turzyniecki | pos=DF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=26|nat=POL||name=[[\u0141ukasz Zejdler]] | pos=MF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=27|nat=POL||name=Daniel Tanzyna | pos=DF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=30|nat=POL||name=[[Mateusz Mo\u017cd\u017ce\u0144]] | pos=MF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=37|nat=POL||name=Kornel Kordas | pos=DF|other=<small>on loan from [[Korona Kielce]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=93|nat=POL||name=[[Przemys\u0142aw Kita]] | pos=FW|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=95|nat=POL||name=Sebastian Zieleniecki | pos=DF|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=99|nat=POL||name=Jakub Miko\u0142ajczak | pos=GK|other=}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014 |nat=EST|name=[[Henrik Ojamaa]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Notable players==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-4}}\n*{{flagicon|Kyrgyzstan}} [[Edgar Bernhardt]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Tadeusz B\u0142achno]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Daniel Bogusz]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Henryk Bolesta]]\n*{{flagicon|Germany}} [[Ulrich Borowka]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Zbigniew Boniek]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Stanis\u0142aw Burzy\u0144ski (footballer)|Stanis\u0142aw Burzy\u0144ski]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Wies\u0142aw Cisek]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Marek Citko]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Ryszard Czerwiec]]\n*{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Jacek Dembi\u0144ski]